Bring out your Shinnyo Nature.
Always keep in mind you are a Shinnyo follower.
Be gentle yet strong.
Avoid selfishness.
Do not bring sadness to others.
Reflect upon yourself before citicizing others.
Avoid gossip.
Listen to the opinions of others.
Put yourself in the place of others.
Be pure.
Always smile when meeting people.
Be a person whom others miss.
Always be honest.
Avoid quarreling.
Be modest.
Treat people with due respect.
Avoid unnecessary chatter.